      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey guys! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy and it is in seriously stunning condition! Honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it\u2014it\u2019s been garage-kept and pampered since day one. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for its next adventure, you\u2019ve gotta see this one. Feel free to shoot me a message!",
