    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a concours-level 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD, featuring the iconic 13B-REW rotary engine with a fully functional sequential twin-turbocharger system. This specimen retains its factory-original kinematics, utilizing a lightweight aluminum double-wishbone suspension and a perfectly balanced 50/50 weight distribution. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 5-speed manual gearbox and a Torsen limited-slip differential, providing visceral mechanical feedback. Meticulously preserved with zero aftermarket modifications, the exterior finish and interior upholstery remain in showroom state. A definitive investment-grade example for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
